  "instructions": [
    "in a large mixing bowl, combine the lamb or beef, onion, garlic, cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "using your hands, mix the ingredients until just combined, being careful not to overmix.",
    "add the lemon juice and mix until the ingredients are just combined.",
    "add the flour and mix until the ingredients are just combined.",
    "using your hands, shape the mixture into small kofte, about 1 1/2 inches in diameter.",
    "heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the kofte to the skillet and cook until browned on all sides and cooked through, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "transfer the kofte to a plate and serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley."
